@prefix bbo:   <https://www.irit.fr/recherches/MELODI/ontologies/BBO#> .
@prefix owl:   <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .
@prefix rdfs:  <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .
@prefix rml: <http://w3id.org/rml/> .
